  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is a multi center, prospective, randomized, parallel study designed to
      compare septal to apical ICD lead placement.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this clinical investigation is to demonstrate that septal
      positioning of the right ventricular defibrillation lead is not inferior to the apical
      positioning in terms of safety and efficacy in a population of ICD recipients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
